3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible sub-category as the paper deals with generative models for image understanding. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible sub-category as the paper deals with generating images from attributes. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is another possible sub-category as the paper uses deep learning methods for generating images.
